    <ab><rs type="conformance">leiden</rs></ab>
    
    <p><note>This section of the guidelines requires revision in concert with DTD changes to realize the
        solution reached in long, painful discussions on the markup and tei lists. What follows now
        is almost surely deprecated.</note></p>
